FT  20 OCT 93 / People: Alexon
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mike Jones has been appointed finance director at ALEXON group; he moves
from the Merchant Retail group, where he was group finance director. He
replaces David Cohen who left on October 1 to join EDS Europe.
In April this year Alexon went through some turmoil as three of its biggest
